questiondata.strat-other: I remembered some by just remembering the first letter of the words. That helped trigger my memory of some words. I also made gestures with my hands to symbolize some words as appropriate. For some reason the gestures were easy to remember and trigger some words such as "ankle, wrist, forehead" etc.
